data.name: labelNoteEditor.Text
data.value:
- Use Right click on images to view menu. - Use double click on each Image to view it in Full-Screen mode. - Also you can load another image. - In normal view mode of image, you can use pipette to determine color statistics.
- If you choose some example, than your task is bring image in the right box to image that located in the left box.

data.name: labelNoteCharacteristics.Text
data.value:
Click "Calculate components" to view components.
Use double click on each Image to view it in Full-Screen mode.
Also you can load another image.
In every component images light color meens that corresponding component take high value, dark conversely.
